{"tid":1796392,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"警民雙方既策略無變，民意就唔會逆轉","createTime":"2019-12-24T14:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T14:57:42.000Z","uid":46933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5ff35d55c6e2479451ccc45d46f112a683e227d","tid":1796392,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"示威者既手段係針對性輕度武力<br />\n除左藍店、黑警、白衣人<br />\n所有無關事者都可以放心睇戲<br />\n商鋪可以正常營業<br />\n<br />\n而黑警則一直用無差別大範圍武器如TG<br />\n所到之處皆無法正常運作<br />\n所有人都只會驚黑警，唔會驚示威者<br />\n<br />\n只要繼續落去，民意只會更加一面倒<br />\n藍絲再反智都唔會食住TG走出去同黑警握手<br />\n<br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80771de3b1a7c267b234847859f416279ad72728","tid":1796392,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/QWnqNYW.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n撞一次，藍變黃"},{"pid":"d9174c6ad5b0bd89c7fa6bc9847ff5999f59482e","tid":1796392,"uid":342786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80771de3b1a7c267b234847859f416279ad72728","tid":1796392,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/QWnqNYW.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n撞一次，藍變黃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6q1LaBj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6q1LaBj.gif&h=d4ae966c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26707649c500e3af72cafc9b60868e08cdd9b43c","tid":1796392,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T14:44:54.000Z","msg":"所有人都只會驚黑警係咪唔包藍絲"},{"pid":"a7ecbe3843a0d434be2ff16079b1c51ff81cd20b","tid":1796392,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26707649c500e3af72cafc9b60868e08cdd9b43c","tid":1796392,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T14:44:54.000Z","msg":"所有人都只會驚黑警係咪唔包藍絲"},"citedBy":0,"r